    public class ExtendedPrimefacesDatatable
extends org.primefaces.component.datatable.DataTable
    Create our own datatable component based on primefaces one, because its impossible to use column sortBy attribute in composite component since EL expression is not evaluated. Issue: http://code.google.com/p/primefaces/issues/detail?id=2930
    Author:
    Ignas
